  <text>
    <body>
      <lg type="sonnet">
        <lg type="1st quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>Like waves float to the shore,</l>
            <l>ends our time together now,</l>
            <l>Everything swaps with what was before,</l>
            <l>In discharge of hard work it will fight forward.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="2nd quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>The birth of <name type="person">Jesus</name>, first time arriving,</l>
            <l>on his way, to grow up being crowned,</l>
            <l>Betrayed decline against his actions,</l>
            <l>Through time his actions confuse people.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="3rd quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>Time destroys his short peak of influence.</l>
          </s>
          <s>
            <l>Hard Search for former beautiful facial expressions</l>
            <l>Just loves on rare things.</l>
          </s>
          <s>
            <l>Nothing works, just his scythe.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="final couplet">
          <s>
            <l>In hopeful times, my words will work,</l>
            <l>esteeming your worth, though his brutal actions.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
